<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id6b093700-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s36"><num value="36">§ 36.</num><heading> Mosquito Creek, South Carolina</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Mosquito Creek, in Colleton County, South Carolina, is declared to be a nonnavigable stream within the meaning of the Constitution and laws of the United States.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id6b093701-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e">(<ref href="/us/act/1917-08-08/ch49/s15">Aug. 8, 1917, ch. 49, § 15</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/40/268">40 Stat. 268</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
